#: plugins.docbook:552 plugins.docbook:871 plugins.docbook:913
#: plugins.docbook:938 plugins.docbook:1377 plugins.docbook:1532
#: plugins.docbook:1903 plugins.docbook:2659 plugins.docbook:4123
#: plugins.docbook:4231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Configuratie"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the configuration page add the directories containing the source code."
msgstr ""
"Op de instellingenpagina voegt u de mappen toe die de broncode bevatten."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: plugins.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backtrace Browser"
msgstr "Backtrace browser"

#. Tag: caption
#: plugins.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Paths in Backtrace browser tool view"
msgstr "Paden in hulpmiddelenweergave van Backtrace browser configureren"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking <guibutton>OK</guibutton> will start indexing. When indexing is "
"finished, open the toolview <guilabel>Backtrace Browser</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Op <guibutton>OK</guibutton> klikken zal indexering starten. Wanneer "
"indexering gereed is, open dan het weergavehulpmiddel <guilabel>Backtrace "
"browser</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now you can load a backtrace from the clipboard (&eg;, when you clicked "
"<guibutton>Copy to Clipboard</guibutton> in &drkonqi;) or from a file."
msgstr ""
"Nu kunt u een backtrace uit het klembord laden (&eg;. wanneer u op "
"<guibutton>Naar klembord kopiëren</guibutton> klikt in &drkonqi;) of uit een "
"bestand."

